                    <comment id="12500434" author="rolandw" created="Thu, 31 May 2007 19:17:47 +0100"  >Literal IPv6 addresses are not and will not be officially supported by HttpClient 3.x. Even if we can fix this specific problem, that does not mean that IPv6 literals will work as expected. For example, domain matching in cookies may or may not do what you expect. We don&amp;#39;t know, and there are no test cases.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
cheers,&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Roland&lt;br/&gt;
</comment>
